Author: strangernumberone
Text: You sound like me for years (minus the kids) before I fell off the corporate ladder and landed on my head. It sounds like you've been carrying a lot and it's sure to burn you out if you don't prioritize yourself a little. If you don't already have a therapist or counselor, I'd recommend one. If I could go back I would do it way before I let it get so bad.
